<!--pages/details/details.wxml-->
<view class="article">
  <view class="article_head">
    <image class="article_headphoto" src="/ative/shareimg/head.jpg"></image>
    <view class="article_user">曾兆育</view>
  </view>
  <view class="article_book">
    <view class="hot_book_box">
      <image src="/ative/shareimg/book2.png" class="book2"></image>
      <view class="book_card">
        <text class="book_name">活着</text>
        <text class="book_writer">余华 | 长篇小说</text>
        <view class="book_core">
          <block wx:for="{{stars}}" wx:key="{{item}}">
            <image class="star-image" src="{{halfSrc}}">
            </image>
          </block>
          <view class="book_core1">10.0</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="article_content">
    <view class="article_text">
      这是一个历尽世间沧桑和磨难老人的人生感言，是一幕演绎人生苦难经历的戏剧。小说的叙述者“我"在年轻时获得了一个游手好闲的职业——去乡间收集民间歌谣。在夏天刚刚来到的季节，遇到那位名叫福贵的老人，听他讲述了自己坎坷的人生经历:地主少爷福贵嗜赌成性，终于赌光了家业，一贫如洗，穷困之中福贵因母亲生病前去求医，没想到半路上被国民党部队抓了壮丁，后被解放军所俘虏，回到家乡他才知道母亲已经过世，妻子家珍含辛茹苦带大了一双儿女但女儿不幸变成了哑巴。
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="article_releasetime">
    <view class="article_time">2021-04-16 14:37</view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="boundary"></view>
<view class="comment">
  <view class="all_comment">共4条评论</view>
  <view class="comment_head">
    <image class="comment_headphoto" src="/ative/shareimg/head.jpg"></image>
    <view class="comment_search_group" bindtap="searchtitle">
      <input class="comment_search_group__input" placeholder="就等你来评论了......" />
    </view>
  </view>
  <block wx:for="{{[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8]}}" wx:key="*this">
    <view class="comment_body">
    <image class="comment_avatars" src="/ative/shareimg/head.jpg"></image>
    <view class="comment_content">
      <view class="comment_name">吃饭吃太多\n</view>
      <view class="comment_details">
